  PIPELINE:
    1. Train MNIST MLPClassifier(128,64) → extract integer weights
    2. Build SRS = [G, τG, τ²G, …] with random 64-bit τ
    3. Commit real MNIST weights: C_real = Σ wᵢ · SRS[i]
